 - Senior Qianyu.

29
00:02:18,989 --> 00:02:21,530
   

30
00:02:25,410 --> 00:02:26,910
Gu Ran.

31
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,729
When is Senior Qianyu's turn?

32
00:02:34,729 --> 00:02:36,010
What?

