I'm curious.

35
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:50,310
How did you fall for Senior Qianyu?

36
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:58,540
At first, I was attracted by the way he looked playing the guitar.

37
00:02:58,540 --> 00:03:01,399
Later, after getting to know him, I learned

38
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:04,560
about his good academic performance and amiable character.

39
